x-sap-shortText: API to manage employees skill information

info.title: Skills Management
info.description:
You can use these APIs to manage the information about employees skills.

 You can find your company's API server in [List of API Servers in SAP SuccessFactors.](https://help.sap.com/viewer/d599f15995d348a1b45ba5603e2aba9b/LATEST/en-US/af2b8d5437494b12be88fe374eba75b6.html)

value.example: Requested entity is not found. Please check the entity in Admin Center > OData API Data Dictionary or contact your system administrator.

post.summary: Add new entity to Role Competency Behavior mapping entity.
post.description: You can use following request to create a new Role Competency Behavior mapping entity to map a behavior to a role through a competency. Behavior is be added to a competency. When this competency is then mapped to a role, the behavior gets mapped to the role through the competency.

value.example: [COE0027]Please add required properties in payload. Required properties status, behaviorMappingEntityNav, competencyNav are missing. You can check which properties are required for an entity in Admin Center > OData API Data Dictionary or the entity metadata.

get.summary: Get entity from Role Competency Behavior mapping entity by key.
get.description: You can use following request to get a Role Competency Behavior mapping entity by externalCode or get all Role Competency Behavior mapping entities of specific role by RoleEntity_externalCode.

parameters.name: $select
parameters.description: Select properties to be returned, see [OData Select](http://docs.oasis-open.org/odata/odata/v4.0/odata-v4.0-part1-protocol.html#_Toc445374620)

value.example: [COE0028]Record for entity RoleCompetencyBehaviorMappingEntity with specific key does not exist. Please check the key value.

put.summary: Update entity in Role Competency Behavior mapping entity by key.
put.description: You can use following request to update an existing Role Competency Behavior mapping entity by externalCode.

value.example: [COE0027]Please add required properties in payload. Required properties status, behaviorMappingEntityNav, competencyNav are missing. You can check which properties are required for an entity in Admin Center > OData API Data Dictionary or the entity metadata.
[COE0028]Record for entity RoleCompetencyBehaviorMappingEntity with specific key does not exist. Please check the key value.

delete.summary: Delete entity from Role Competency Behavior mapping entity
delete.description: You can use following request to delete an existing Role Competency Behavior mapping entity by externalCode.

value.example: RoleCompetencyBehaviorMappingEntity need a key value in DELETE operation.
[COE0028]Record for entity RoleCompetencyBehaviorMappingEntity with specific key does not exist. Please check the key value.
